thread.title: Ali
thread.title_full: TAXIBOX mobile self-storage reviewed by Ali

author: Ali
title: Ali
text:
Mobile self storage is often a better alternative to traditional moving or storing. Taxi box were easy to use, with good online and phone service. We store things, picked things up from our box, and had the boxes re delivered.
Try to give them notice if you want pick up/delivery on Saturdays. Otherwise perfect.
